🤲 SafeHands — Always There

> "Because they cared for us — now it's our turn."

SafeHands is a mobile app designed to support 
elderly people living alone — ensuring their 
safety, health and emotional wellbeing — always.

---

## 💡 The Problem

In India today —
- 15 Crore people are above 60 years old
- 3 Crore elderly people live completely alone
- They struggle daily with medicines, meals 
  and emergencies
- Existing apps are too complicated for them
- No app offers regional language training

> No elder should feel alone, unheard or unsafe.

---

## 🚀 Our Solution

SafeHands provides 6 powerful services —

| Feature | Description |
|---|---|
| 💊 Medicine Reminders | Timely alerts — never miss a dose |
| 🍱 Food & Grocery | Healthy meals delivered to door |
| 🆘 Emergency SOS | One tap alerts family instantly |
| 🚶 Caretaker Visits | Verified caretakers for walks |
| 💬 Companionship | Talk to someone when lonely |
| ❤️ Health Check-ins | Regular health monitoring |

