## 🗺️ Roadmap

### Phase 1 — Build (Month 1-4)
- Build SafeHands app
- Register company
- Sign pharmacy & food partners
- Create regional language training

### Phase 2 — Launch (Month 5-7)
- Train first 10 elderly users
- Launch WhatsApp campaign
- Onboard first 50 customers
- Go Live in Hyderabad!

### Phase 3 — Sprint (Month 8-12)
- Fix app issues from feedback
- Start referral program
- Reach 340 customers
- Expand to next city

