## ⚠️ Key Risks & Mitigation

| Risk | Mitigation |
|---|---|
| Elderly reject app | Personal training in regional language |
| Medicine delay | 3 backup pharmacy partners |
| User dropout | Weekly check-in calls |
| Competition | Unique regional language training |

